cs.NA, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.SI 

The paper discusses optimization methods in machine learning, signal and image processing, and communications, which are all relevant to the sub-categories of numerical analysis (cs.NA), machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), information theory (cs.IT), and social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper specifically focuses on the practical implementation of the forward-backward splitting method, which is commonly used in these fields.
